            <![CDATA[
                    <img src="https://vervallsweg.github.io/cast-web/media/posts/4/" alt="" />
                <p>So, you have a problem with cast-web? Don't worry!</p>
<p>First check the <a href="#INTERNAL_LINK#/post/11" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">FAQ</a>.</p>
<p>Then have a quick look at the <a href="https://community.smartthings.com/t/release-cast-web-0-2-chromecast-device-handler-smartapps/88038" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">SmartThings community forum thread</a>.</p>
<p>If you cannot find the answer there, just signup and ask your question on <a href="https://community.smartthings.com/t/release-cast-web-0-2-chromecast-device-handler-smartapps/88038">the forum</a>.</p>
